sentences: Kim Han-gil (Korean: 김한길; born July 26, 1988) better known by his stage name Zick Jasper (직 재스퍼), formerly 5Zic, is a South Korean rapper and beatboxer.
He made his recording debut with the single "Beautiful Day" just before his debut with the group.
He is currently signed under Jungle Entertainment.
